@baseUrl = http://localhost:8000

### Health Check
GET {{baseUrl}}/hello

### Full-text Search - Single Keyword
GET {{baseUrl}}/legal-documents/fulltext?q=contract&top=10

### Full-text Search - All Keywords
GET {{baseUrl}}/legal-documents/fulltext/all?keywords=contract,agreement,2023&top=10

### Full-text Search - Any Keywords
GET {{baseUrl}}/legal-documents/fulltext/any?keywords=contract,agreement&top=10

### Full-text Search - Relevance Score
GET {{baseUrl}}/legal-documents/fulltext/relevant?keywords=contract,agreement&top=10

### Create Legal Document
POST {{baseUrl}}/legal-documents
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "title": "Sample Contract",
    "content": "This is a sample contract agreement...",
    "documentType": "contract",
    "metadata": {
        "author": "John Doe",
        "version": "1.0",
        "tags": ["contract", "agreement", "sample"]
    }
}

### Generate Sample Data
GET {{baseUrl}}/generate-fake-legal-documents